title: States’ Push to Protect Kids Online Could Remake the Internet
description: New age restrictions for minors on sites like TikTok and Pornhub could also hinder adults’ access to online services.

title: Echoes of History in New National Push to Shield Children Online
description: In the 1990s, the U.S. government limited what young people could see online, but lost a court fight challenging those rules. Now it’s happening again.

title: Elon Musk: SpaceX’s Out-of-Control Starship Struggled to Self-Destruct
description: In an update on the first flight of the most powerful rocket ever, Elon Musk offered a timeline of what went wrong while staying optimistic about forthcoming launches.
